jsn S No.763_1983 IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY ORDINARY ORIGINAL SIDE JURISDICTION SUIT NO.763 OF 1983 Shri Raju Naraindas Amarnani & Ors.

Plaintiffs Vs. Bon Bihari Vishnu Nimbkar & Anr.

Defendants Mr. K H Mody, Adv. i/b. R G Sheth, Adv. for plaintiff No.5. None for the defendants. CORAM : MRS. ROSHAN DALVI, J. DATE : 30

th April, 2015.

P.C. : Consent decree has been passed. The original consent decree has been issued to the plaintiff No.5. The plaintiff No.5 has applied for a fresh consent decree. Only the duplicate consent decree is now available on record. The duplicate consent decree cannot be issued to any party. A certified copy of the duplicate consent decree shall be issued to plaintiff No.5.

( ROSHAN DALVI, J. )
